The Tian Guo Marching Band participated in the 28th Chiayi City International Band Festival on Saturday, December 21, 2019. Around 50 other bands also participated in the annual event, including from Japan, France, Germany, Belgium, Thailand, Hong Kong, and Taiwan.

This is the ninth time that Falun Dafa practitioners have been invited to bring the Tian Guo Marching Band to the festival. This year, the event started on December 20 and will finish on January 1, 2020. More than 80 concerts are scheduled during this time, and the audience is expected to be in the hundreds of thousands.
